
Menu:
- Press ESC to quit (a swell option).
- Press Space to play:
	- Press Space to generate a random shape.
	- Move with WASD and use the mouse to pan.
	- Left click picks up a shape if it's within range.
	- Mouse wheel moves a held shape closer/farther.
	- Right click held and drag sends the shape in the intersected look direction.
	- Right click held + mouse wheel changes the speed of the thrown shape.
	- Press ESC to go back to the menu.
